PORefreshBuyerCubes_ST is a SecurityClass
	description is "Access Buyer Refresh Cubes"
	Access Rights
	
		PurchaseOrder BusinessClass
			is accessible
				for RefreshBuyerCubes
				when (Company.SecurityGroupAllowsAccess)

		RefreshBuyerCubes MenuItem for BuyerMenu Menu
			is accessible
				for all actions
				unconditionally
				
		RefreshPurchasingCubes MenuItem for PurchasingManagerMenu Menu
			is accessible
				for all actions
				unconditionally
				